---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const lastUpdated = new Intl.DateTimeFormat(undefined, {
  year: "numeric",
  month: "long",
  day: "2-digit",
}).format(new Date());
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | CalcHub"
  description="CalcHub privacy policy. We are committed to protecting your privacy. No personal data is collected or stored."
>
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-4xl">
    <div class="text-sm text-muted">
      <a class="link-accent" href="/">← Back to homepage</a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-10">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">Website: CalcHub</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        CalcHub is committed to protecting your privacy. Our calculators are designed to work without accounts, without ads, and without collecting personal
        information. This policy explains what we do (and do not) collect when you use our website.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-10 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl">1. Introduction</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        CalcHub provides free online calculators for everyday decisions. We aim to keep the experience fast, simple, and privacy-friendly. We do not require
        registration and we do not ask you to provide personal details to use the tools.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl">2. What We Do NOT Collect</h2>
      <div class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        <p>No account or registration is required.</p>
        <p>No calculation inputs or results are stored.</p>
        <p>No personal data is sold to third parties.</p>
        <p>All calculations happen in your browser only.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl">3. What We May Collect Automatically</h2>
      <div class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        <p>
          We may collect anonymous page view data to understand overall usage (for example: which pages are popular, and whether the site is performing well).
        </p>
        <p>Browser type and device type (in an aggregated, anonymous form).</p>
        <p>No personal identification should be possible from this data.</p>
        <p>
          This may be collected via Google Analytics configured in anonymous mode.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl">4. Cookies Policy</h2>
      <div class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        <p>We use minimal analytics cookies only (if analytics is enabled).</p>
        <p>No advertising cookies.</p>
        <p>No personal tracking cookies.</p>
        <p>
          You can disable cookies in your browser settings. Most browsers allow you to block cookies entirely, clear cookies, or limit third-party cookies.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl">5. Third Party Services</h2>
      <div class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        <p>
          Google Analytics — anonymous traffic data only (if enabled).
        </p>
        <p>
          Exchange rate API — used by our currency converter to fetch exchange rates. No personal data is sent.
        </p>
        <p>
          Google Fonts — used for font delivery only.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl">6. Childrens Privacy</h2>
      <div class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        <p>CalcHub is safe for all ages.</p>
        <p>We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl">7. Policy Changes</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        We may update this policy occasionally to reflect improvements or changes to the website. Please check this page for the latest version.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl">8. Contact</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        If you have privacy questions, contact us at <a class="link-accent" href="mailto:privacy@calchub.com">privacy@calchub.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="mt-10 text-sm text-muted">
      <a class="link-accent" href="/">← Back to homepage</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
